================================================================================
(1) Introduction
================================================================================

Solves for decoherence of a central spin in a spin bath.

Includes:
- Cluster correlation expansion
- Special methods for donor qubits

Notes:
- Most code in C++
- Based on old code "cce" -> "SpinDecoherence" developed in 2011-2013
- This version started 19/05/2013
- Some methods were originally written in Fortran by Tania Monteiro

* Seto Balian 02/09/2013

================================================================================
(2) Installation
================================================================================

System requirements:
- Unix-like OS with c++ compiler (g++ 4.4.7 or above recommended).
- Lapack (optional)

Uses (all included):
- Eigen: Open-source linear algebra package
  http://eigen.tuxfamily.org
- argvparser: Open-source command line option parser by Michael Hanke
  http://mih.voxindeserto.de/argvparser.html

