================================================================================
(4) Getting help
================================================================================

- For descriptions (or definitions) of the classes see the start of
  header files (.h extension)
- Source files (.cpp extension) may contain more information, usually geared
  more towards implementation
- See $(PROJECTPATH)/main/  for the 'main' source files used to build the
  executables in $(PROJECTPATH)/bin/
- Resources for the executables, such as sample input files can be found in
  $(PROJECTPATH)/bin/

